description: Ringside Grill is bringing gourmet eats to the streets of Norwalk and you can believe that this scrumptious American cuisine is the talk of the town.Passion and care are the main ingredients of their wonderful menu, which features foods that will warm your heart and soul as you’re invited to indulge in your favorite comfort fare, like Tacos, Pizza, Chicken ‘n Waffles, Steaks, Burgers, and more!So come swing by Ringside Grill, to graze on the tastiest grub in Norwalk, and you too will praise that this food is “Always Fresh, Always Fast, Always Delicious!”
name: Ringside Grill
